text: Lara Lea Yunaska Trump (born October 12, 1982) is an American television producer and political strategist. She served as the co-chair of the Republican National Committee from March to December 2024. She is married to Eric Trump, the third child of Donald Trump, the 45th president and 47th president-elect.
